snippet.title: First Dwarf - Official Teaser Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
Take a peek at the fantasy world, gameplay, and mech combat action of First Dwarf in this teaser trailer for the upcoming action RPG from Star Drifters. First Dwarf will be available on PC, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5, and Xbox Series X/S.

#gamescom
